This pattern becomes even more striking when we look at artificial intelligence.
</prosody>

<break time="1s"/>

<prosody rate="slow" volume="loud">
These are some of the <emphasis level="strong">smartest people</emphasis> working on what might be the <emphasis level="strong">most important technology</emphasis> of our time...
